title: #92Noon! Paul Charchian in for PA! New NCAA ruling, the NFL and COVID, and a lesson about Hedy Lamarr
description: Charch fills in for PA, he talks about the new Supreme Court ruling against the NCAA, the NFL and its stance on COVID Vaccines, Brian Oake and Brianne join for a segment to talk about their upcoming events, and Charch tells the story of Hedy Lamarr.
